### BioMart Annotation

RNA-seq gene annotation is download from [BioMart](http://www.ensembl.org/biomart/martview/b50484329e8deb4e57a659564604e9f5)

```
Dataset:
  Human genes (GRCh38.p12)
Attributes:
  Gene stable ID
  Transcript stable ID
  Gene start (bp)
  Gene end (bp)
  Transcript start (bp)
  Transcript end (bp)
  Transcription start site (TSS)
  Gene type
  GO term accession
  GO term name
  HGNC symbol
```
